{"type":"message","id":"a3385c1b","parentId":"4733c35b","timestamp":"2026-06-13T12:32:21.127Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking for product selection (选品) and specifically wants profit-focused products (利润款). Based on my MEMORY.md and SOUL.md, I'm the TK product selection master focused on TikTok product analysis. I have context about the selection SOP v7.0 which covers Vietnam and Thailand markets.\n\nLet me think about what I know:\n- My core SOP is about selecting black horse products from Shopee → validating with TikTok → sourcing from 1688\n- Entry thresholds: gross margin ≥70% (hard requirement), price floor $3.0+\n- I have cron jobs set up for Vietnam and Thailand selection\n- Previous scans found that hair accessories (饰品) category mathematically cannot satisfy both $3.0+ price and 70% margin\n\n\n- I should clarify what product category and market they're targeting since my cron jobs focus on Vietnam and Thailand hair accessories, but they might want something different or need me to scan first.","thinkingSignature":"4dc2d79512bc775ab3a9b9a2064d083d2aff4f127c4c5cbd94206b9f967e6247"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n收到！选利润款。\n\n不过我需要确认几个信息：\n\n**1. 目标市场是？**\n- 越南 VN\n- 泰国 TH\n- 还是两个都要\n\n**2. 产品类目方向？**\n上次复盘确认饰品品类数学上不满足 $3.0 + 70% 毛利率双重门槛，这次优先扫：\n- 美妆工具\n- 厨房小件\n- 母婴用品\n- 宠物用品\n\n还是你有其他方向？\n\n**3. 价格底线确认？**\n- $3.0 以上（≥105k VND 越南 / ≥150 THB 泰国）\n- 毛利率 ≥70% 硬指标\n\n确认后我立即开扫。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":57568,"output":340,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":57908,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781353931830,"responseId":"067c80cc6432423e4e05bb42f5b2ce71"}}
