{"type":"message","id":"1689fce2","parentId":"582691e3","timestamp":"2026-06-13T13:16:04.356Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is pushing back on the rigid SOP and wants a more dynamic approach. They're saying:\n\n1. A single price adjustment won't work\n2. Need a dynamic \"algorithm\" mechanism for selecting potential profit products\n3. Can't completely lock down profit margins\n4. Let products in first, human reviews the selected products early stage\n5. Later profit comes from: expanding product range, bundle combos, SKU improvements, complementary products\n\nThey're asking me to first explain how to change the SOP/strategy.\n\nLet me think about what a dynamic mechanism would look like:\n\n**Current v7.0 rigid approach:**\n- Hard cutoff: price ≥ $3.0 AND margin ≥ 70%\n- Any product not meeting both = discarded\n\n\n- \n**Dynamic approach I'm thinking through:**\n- Use multiple signals like Shopee monthly sales, 7-day momentum, rating, review count, TikTok trend data, and 1688 cost to create a composite \"potential score\" instead of binary pass/fail\n- Tier products into categories like S/A/B/C for human review priority, where early stage focuses on potential products even with moderate margins and human filtering, and later stage relies on bundling and SKU expansion for actual profit realization\n- Consider 1688 cost as a leading indicator since TikTok sells in USD but Shopee dominance in VN/TH means prices are already set by competitors, so our only leverage is keeping procurement costs low enough to maintain margin\n\nThe user wants me to explain the proposed changes first before implementing them, so I should outline this dynamic approach and get alignment before updating anything.\n","thinkingSignature":"ebcfeac4d02d49eea572786260ffeebd0bf0559cbc1f25d09fb9274c9d196ea1"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n好，说说我的理解。\n\n---\n\n## 动态选品机制（草案）\n\n### 核心逻辑：潜力优先，利润追踪\n\n**三个阶段，各有重心：**\n\n**① 入选阶段 — 宽进**\n- 先用 Shopee 销量×增长率×评分 算出「市场热度分」\n- 毛利率 ≥40% 即可进入候选（不是 ≥70%）\n- 价格 $1.5+ 即可（不是 $3.0+）\n- TikTok 有同款 → 加权，爆款信号更强\n- 目的是**让更多产品进来**，不要在入口就卡死\n\n**② 初筛阶段 — 人工把关**\n- 我筛完的结果先发给你看，不是直接写飞书\n- 你人工过一遍：图片、材质、差异化可行性\n- 通过的品 → 进入备选池\n\n**③ 利润实现 — 靠后端**\n- 毛利兑现不靠单品定价，靠：\n  - **拓品**：同一方向多款进货，摊低成本\n  - **组合**：2-3个关联品打包卖，提升客单价\n  - **SKU改造**：变体扩展（颜色/尺寸/包装量）\n  - **互补品搭配**：发夹+发绳+发带一套，提升整单利润\n\n---\n\n### 调整后的筛选漏斗\n\n```\nShopee热销 → 热度分排序 → 毛利≥40%入选 → TikTok验证\n→ 候选池 → 你人工过 → 备选池 → 1688找货源\n→ 组合方案 → 上架\n```\n\n---\n\n**问题是：现在 Shopee 数据够不够支撑这个动态评分？**\n\nShopee 能给的信号：\n- 月销量 / 7天销量（量）\n- 增长率（势）\n- 评分 / 评价数（质）\n- 上架时间（新旧）\n- 价格（竞争度）\n\nTikTok 能给的信号：\n- 是否有同款在跑（爆款信号）\n- 周趋势（增长还是衰退）\n\n这几个信号我可以做成**加权评分模型**，输出一个「潜力分」给你排序参考，而不是二极管 yes/no。\n\n---\n\n**你现在要做的：**\n\n1. 确认这个方向 OK\n2. 告诉我你的排序权重倾向：\n   - 销量权重更高（爆过的是真的爆）？\n   - 增长率权重更高（涨势猛的才是黑马）？\n   - TikTok 信号权重更高（有同款跑才是验证过）？\n\n方向对了，我来写新的 SOP。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":58171,"output":834,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":59005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1781356552158,"responseId":"067c8b08965727b772d11f6f8f0bbd27"}}
