{"type":"message","id":"ce038b6a","parentId":"957fb120","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:02:51.873Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update MEMORY.md to reflect the SOP v8.0 change. Let me also update the cron configuration if needed. But first, let me start scanning Vietnam hair accessories with the new approach.\n\nLet me scan using the Sorftime API. I need to use curl to call the API directly.","thinkingSignature":"2294774a0418e318da3a8ddc129b31b6a86887f7d6e9112cb26d6715adaab122"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSOP v8.0 写好了，核心变化：\n- 毛利率 70% 硬卡 → **≥40% 入选参考指标**\n- 价格底线 $3.0 → **$1.5**\n- 新增**人工审核环节**（结果发给你看，不直接写飞书）\n- 利润靠后端组合结构实现\n\n现在开扫越南发饰：\n\n**扫描参数：**\n- 站点：VN 越南\n- 类目：nodeId=11035861（Kẹp tóc 发夹）\n- 月销量 ≥ 50\n- 价格 ≥ 45,000 VND（$1.5）\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\n\n先扫第一轮，把候选池搞出来给你审：\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_757b5dd8d5da4569a86f4cb1","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"sleep 1 && curl -s -X POST \"https://mcp.sorftime.com/\" \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H \"accept: application/json, text/event-stream\" \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":45000,\"page\":1}},\"id\":1}'","timeout":30}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":52,"output":382,"cacheRead":63168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":63602,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781359363502,"responseId":"067c9604221ce0359f9096ef2ae20d6c"}}
