{"type":"message","id":"27922ad4","parentId":"0bdaa6fa","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:11:03.807Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Missing 6/10, 6/11, 6/12, 6/13 daily notes. Let me create them all, then update MEMORY.md, then continue with the candidate pool.\n\nI need to write daily notes for 6/10-6/13. These are short notes about what happened each day based on what I know from the MEMORY.md promoted content and my context.\n\nFrom MEMORY.md:\n- 6/10: Not much info, cron runs happened but with issues\n- 6/11: Same\n- 6/12: Same  \n- 6/13: The big v8.0 strategy session with HALEI today\n\n\n- Now I'm looking at the MEMORY.md file to understand the v8.0 framework and what's stored there.\n","thinkingSignature":"fde1e195908445c975a4560b40042cbe7ef9183cbc2d790d5130a444b2369bc0"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_72bd889fa78147cf93914c32","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/halei/workspace-tts/MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":4689,"output":201,"cacheRead":73285,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78175,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1781359854556,"responseId":"067c97ef06b4d393e57ec3478aea6ca1"}}
{"type":"message","id":"07f54719","parentId":"27922ad4","timestamp":"2026-06-13T14:11:03.994Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_72bd889fa78147cf93914c32","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# MEMORY.md - 长期记忆\n\n每次醒来都会读这个文件。惜字如金，只留真正重要的。\n\n## 用户信息\n- 用户通过飞书与 TK 选品大师对话\n- 代号：TK 选品大师（TTS Agent）\n- 专注：TikTok 选品相关的分析和建议\n\n## 索引\n\n> `memory/` 下的文件索引。新建文件时在此添加条目。\n\n- YYYY-MM-DD.md: 每日日志\n\n## 工作流\n\n### 选品写入流程\n- 每次用 sorftime MCP 查完选品数据后，**直接写入飞书多维表**\n- 写入目标多维表：https://bytedance.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n- app_token: AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n- table_id: tblHU2do30jzinJT\n- 写入前确认 bot 已有「可编辑」权限（如遇写入被拒，需在多维表界面分享添加 bot）\n\n### 妙手ERP采集流程（选品→上架）\n- **Skill**: miaoshou-erp-source-import\n- **作用**: 把选品好的产品（1688/AliExpress链接）采集到妙手ERP公共采集箱\n- **凭证配置**: skills/miaoshou-erp-source-import/resources/config.json\n- **流程**: 用户提供货源链接 → 调用 fetch_item API → 返回 detailId\n- **后续**: detailId 可用于查询/编辑/认领到TikTok\n\n### 选品核心逻辑（v7.0 越泰黑马拦截策略）\n\n**核心策略：Shopee 验证热销 → TikTok 趋势确认 → 1688 利润终选**\n\n数据源：Shopee（主要）→ TikTok（验证）→ 1688（货源）→ 飞书多维表格\n\n**入场门槛（越南）：**\n- 月销量 ≥ 50单\n- 7天销量 ≥ 月销量×15%\n- 评分 ≥ 4.0\n- 上架时间 ≤ 6个月\n- 好评率 ≥ 90%\n- 毛利率 ≥ 40%（越南固定成本≈45%）\n- 1688采购价 ≤ ¥5\n\n**入场门槛（泰国）：**\n- 同越南，但毛利率门槛 ≥ 50%\n\n**推荐等级：**\n- S级：毛利率≥60% + 7天销量≥500 + TK有同款 → 立即采购50-100件\n- A级：毛利率≥40% + 增长≥30% + TK有同款 → 正常采购30-50件\n- B级：毛利率≥40% + TK有同款 → 正常采购30-50件\n- C级：其他达标 → 观望\n\n## 技术配置\n\n### sorftime MCP\n- key: rhblyi90suxqqwfnnwzwy2tdvuhwqt09\n- 文件路径：/tmp/sorftime_key.txt\n\n### API 调用（curl 直调）\n```\ncurl -s -X POST 'https://mcp.sorftime.com/' \\\n  -H \"Authorization: Bearer $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)\" \\\n  -H 'accept: application/json, text/event-stream' \\\n  -H 'Content-Type: application/json' \\\n  -d '{\"jsonrpc\":\"2.0\",\"method\":\"tools/call\",\"params\":{\"name\":\"shopee_product_search\",\"arguments\":{\"site\":\"VN\",\"nodeId\":\"11035861\",\"monthSaleVolumeRangeMin\":50,\"priceRangeMin\":20000,\"page\":1}},\"id\":1}'\n```\n\n### 类目ID\n- 越南发夹：11035861（Kẹp tóc）\n- 泰国发饰：11046516（เครื่องประดับ）\n\n### 飞书多维表写入要点\n- **app_token 必须用完整值**：`AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd`\n- **MultiSelect 字段**用数组格式：`[\"Sorftime-TK数据\"]`\n- **SingleSelect 字段**用选项名字符串：`\"S级\"`、`\"A级\"`、`\"无\"`、`\"已采集\"` 等\n- **批量写入**用 `batch_create`，单条用 `create`\n\n## Cron 任务（v7.0）\n- TK选品-越南黑马-v7.0：每天 9、12、15、18、21点（cron id: 6ee6a981）\n- TK选品-泰国黑马-v7.0：每天 9、12、15、18、21点（cron id: dde46f87）\n\n## 文档索引\n\n- SOP（本地）: /home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v7.0.md\n- 飞书多维表: https://bytedance.feishu.cn/base/AKppbAeyXanToTsVl6ScxO5QnZd\n\n## 已知限制\n- API 连续调用过快会报 Authentication required，等待3秒重试即可\n- 越南 TikTok 带货视频数据基本为空，不用视频数量作为筛选条件\n- Shopee 数据粒度为7天/30天，无24小时数据，用 MonthlySalesGrowth 和 SalesCountOf7D 替代\n- VN Shopee 产品搜索 nodeId 不稳定，先用 shopee_category_search_from_name 确认 ID\n\n## 已知偏好\n- 选品逻辑以跟品为主，爆什么跟什么，简单直接\n- 差异化手段：套装组合、变体扩展\n\n## Promoted From Short-Term Memory (2026-06-10)\n\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:16:19 -->\n- 关键发现（与上午12:33一致）: **越南发饰市场整体下行** — 所有Top产品周环比均为负增长（-32%至-39%）; **无KOL带货** — VN站点带货视频数据返回空; **价格带错位** — 越南发饰主流价位在VND 9,000-49,000（≈$0.4-$2.0），低于SOP $1.5最低门槛; **毛利率无法达标** — 3个通过价格筛选产品，毛利率分别为 -481.7%、-19.6%、26.4%，全部低于70%红线 [score=0.806 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:16-19]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:38:40 -->\n- 待观察: 越南发饰市场可能存在季节性下行（6月为淡季？）; 建议关注泰国TH站点是否有更好的黑马信号; 本次扫描确认：越南发饰品类无法同时满足$1.5+价格和70%毛利率两个SOP门槛 [score=0.806 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:38-40]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:49:51 -->\n- 待观察: 越南发饰市场可能存在季节性下行（6月为淡季？）; 建议关注泰国TH站点是否有更好的黑马信号; 建议下次扫描加入\"增长率>0\"硬过滤 [score=0.806 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:49-51]\n\n## Promoted From Short-Term Memory (2026-06-11)\n\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:11:13 -->\n- 扫描结果（第2次）: 搜索产品：100+ 个（多关键词扫描）; 通过$1.5+价格筛选：3个; 推荐等级：全C级（无S/A/B级爆款） [score=0.820 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:11-13]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:22:25 -->\n- 通过筛选的3个产品: | ProductId | 产品 | 售价(VND) | 月销量 | 增长率 | 1688价格 | 毛利率 | |-----------|------|----------|-------|--------|----------|--------| | 1733133706895197735 | Bộ 136 Chiếc Dây Cột Tóc | 45,000 | 23,936 | -32% | ¥69 | -481.7% | | 1731984802588690363 | Kẹp Tóc Lì Đơn Giản | 37,536 | 21,758 | -38.8% | ¥8 | -19.6% | [score=0.820 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:22-25]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:26:26 -->\n- 通过筛选的3个产品: | 1732311961339659361 | Kẹp tóc càng cua 6 Răng | 49,000 | 4,046 | -34.2% | ¥4 | 26.4% | [score=0.820 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:26-26]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:29:31 -->\n- 写入飞书多维表格: 记录ID：recvlQ6ClXUS6v、recvlQ6MJjJ3fP、recvlQ6MJ7Hhtd（3条）; 采集状态：待审核; 推荐等级：全C级 [score=0.820 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:29-31]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:43:46 -->\n- 技术笔记: tiktok_category_report：返回周销量数据（无24小时数据，SOP要求与实际数据存在粒度差异）; tiktok_product_trend：返回周销量趋势，\"新增带货视频数\"字段对VN站点返回空; tiktok_product_video：VN站点普遍返回\"该产品暂无带货达人视频\"; 1688价格：¥3-45（人民币），换算美元约$0.4-$6.2 [score=0.820 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:43-46]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:6:8 -->\n- TK选品-越南黑马拦截-v6.0 Cron 执行（第2次 15:03）: 执行时间：2026-06-07 15:03; 数据源：Sorftime MCP API（mcporter sorftime-mcp）; 站点：越南VN（关键词：hair clip, scrunchie, headband, hair band, hair tie, hair accessory） [score=0.820 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:6-8]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-07.md:34:35 -->\n- 报告已发送: 飞书消息ID：om_x100b6d7b2b29d4a4c0509720f5555fc（第二次报告）; 发送时间：2026-06-07 15:05 [score=0.810 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-07.md:34-35]\n\n## Promoted From Short-Term Memory (2026-06-12)\n\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:26:27 -->\n- 待验证: 越南发夹 nodeId=11035861 搜索（昨天报错，需再测）; 泰国发饰 nodeId=11046516 搜索（已测，有数据） [score=0.815 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:26-27]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:47:49 -->\n- 改进方向: 停发饰品类，换美妆工具/厨房小件/母婴/宠物; 价格底线提至$3.0; 先用 shopee_category_trend 看类目增长再扫产品（省配额） [score=0.815 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:47-49]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:64:66 -->\n- 当前状态（15:22）: 两个cron已disable，等HALEI拍板汇报频率后重建; SOP/ SOUL/ MEMORY 均已更新; 等HALEI一句话 [score=0.815 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:64-66]\n\n## Promoted From Short-Term Memory (2026-06-13)\n\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:38:40 -->\n- 失败原因: B类（品类方向）：越南发饰数学上不可能同时满足$1.5售价+70%毛利 → 约60%; C类（SOP理解）：没有严格执行$1.5价格底线，白耗API配额 → 约25%; 其他（API报错/工具链）→ 约15% [score=0.869 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:38-40]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:60:61 -->\n- 汇报节奏（写进SOUL）: 每周日晚20:00前汇报; 内容：扫描次数/配额消耗/通过品数/等级分布/0产出也要报 [score=0.869 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:60-61]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:69:71 -->\n- 技术备忘: curl 调API：Bearer token 从 /tmp/sorftime_key.txt 读取; API URL：https://mcp.sorftime.com/; 注意：curl 里 key 要用 $(cat /tmp/sorftime_key.txt)，不能硬编码带…的字符 [score=0.869 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:69-71]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:10:11 -->\n- SOP v7.0 重写: 新增泰国独立 cron（nodeId=11046516）; 文档：/home/halei/workspace-tts/docs/SOP-v7.0.md [score=0.837 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:10-11]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:14:16 -->\n- Cron 任务重建: 删除旧的越南 v6.0 cron（id: 5c75bbb4）; 新建越南 v7.0 cron（id: 6ee6a981）— 每天9/12/15/18/21点; 新建泰国 v7.0 cron（id: dde46f87）— 每天9/12/15/18/21点 [score=0.837 recalls=0 avg=0.620 source=memory/2026-06-09.md:14-16]\n<!-- openclaw-memory-promotion:memory:memory/2026-06-09.md:19:22 -->\n- API 验证结果: shopee_product_search：✅ VN/TH 站点可用，支持 nodeId/价格/月销量/评分过滤; shopee_category_search_from_name：✅ 可查类目ID; ali1688_similar_product：✅ 返回货源+价格+